rows.label: bf11320100_0012
rows.name:
Even armless,
a guy like that will just bring you more trouble.

rows.label: bf11320100_0020
rows.name: I just didn't want to kill him here.

rows.label: bf11320100_0030
rows.name:
He may be a scumbag,
but... it seems like my mother was indebted to him...

rows.label: bf11320100_0060
rows.name:
On second thought,
maybe I will pay a visit to that flagship.
